parameters: \n<Polteghost>You think you can have everything you want? Not this book!
\n<Dwayne>Well, that's better! We go to ruins and get the last
book and then get the mirror.
\n<Zarie>It will take time if we'll go back to the Doom Forest.
Let's take the shortcut in the West part of the ruins.
\n<Zarie>Yes! I am sure. We just have to take North then East, that
will be the West part of the ruins.
\n<Philip>Let's go, there is no time to waste.
\n<Dwayne>I think we need that mattock on our journey.
